item.title: Help!when i run a v5 client winrar it says
item.dc:creator: @CoonHunter CoonHunter
item.description:
@CoonHunter wrote:

It means the cache is missing. It reads it like the new cache was uploaded and your using old client, so it wants you to reboot to load the “new” client. This means that the programmer who edited the client, made it basically like the webclient, and never told it to download the cache.
